metadata.name: Sarah
metadata.description:
The name of this collection is Kooch . Kooch means migration. People who leave their homeland with thousands of hopes and aspirations. For this purpose, I chose a kind of doe that migrates a lot.
Sarah has recently gotten married
At this age she should subsequently have thousands of wishes, but fear and anxiety replace wishes. Because she has to leave her hometown in order to have a better future, she also has to start a new marriage life too. These events may seem difficult to a young girl in her early young age. She is hesitant. She does not know whether she made the right decision or not!
Size: 24/3 MG
width: 1490
Height: 2500
